PC PC_Panda2@PandaEatsAtABar
operator OpEats.IntChoice
process PandaEatsAtABar@OpEats
atom :'shoots'
atom :'leaves'
skip SKIP
op_connector OpEats->shoots
op_connector OpEats->leaves
op_connector OpEats->SKIP
reference RefPandaEats
after shoots->RefPandaEats
after leaves->RefPandaEats
ref_connector RefPandaEats->PandaEatsAtABar
